The Crimson Fork â€“ Restaurant Menu Website

A simple and elegant restaurant menu webpage built using HTML, CSS, and Font Awesome icons.
This project displays a stylish two-column menu layout with smooth animations and a modern UI.

Features
- Responsive Layout
- Split into eft and right column sections.
- Menu categories: Starters, Main Courses, Sides, Desserts, Beverages.

Custom Styling

- Dark-blue header and footer.
- Red accent color (`#e63946`) for prices and headings.
- Clean background and readable fonts.

 Animations

- Left side slides in from the left
- Right side slides in from the right

Hover Effects

- Restaurant name grows and changes color on hover.
- Icons increase size and change color when hovered.

Font Awesome Icons

Used for social media icons in the footer.



Technologies Used

| Technology       | Purpose                     |
| ---------------- | --------------------------- |
| **HTML5**        | Structure of the webpage    |
| **CSS3**         | Styling, animations, layout |
| **Font Awesome** | Icons for social media      |
| **Flexbox**      | Aligning menu sections      |



