How to Run the Project

1. Download or clone the project folder.
2. Make sure both `index.html` and `style.css` are in the same directory.
3. Open **index.html** in any modern web browser (Chrome, Edge, Firefox).

That's it â€” the restaurant menu will load instantly!

Customization

You can easily modify:

- Menu items
- Colors
- Animations
- Restaurant name and tagline
- Font styles

Just edit the `index.html` and `style.css` files.

